            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container marketing">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="img-fluid" src="https://tagmefy.com/static/images/icon1.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
          <h2>Register lost or found object!</h2>
          <p>Free, simple and fast registration. Select category, add picture and short description.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="img-fluid" src="https://tagmefy.com/static/images/icon3.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
          <h2>Select auto-matched items!</h2>
          <p>Our smart search agent will do the magic and show most relevant matches to your lost or found request.</p>
        </div>
